CLASS lhc_item DEFINITION INHERITING FROM cl_abap_behavior_handler.

  PRIVATE SECTION.

    METHODS setTotalValue FOR DETERMINE ON MODIFY
      IMPORTING keys FOR Item~setTotalValue.
    METHODS setTotalAmount FOR DETERMINE ON MODIFY
      IMPORTING keys FOR Item~setTotalAmount.

ENDCLASS.

CLASS lhc_item IMPLEMENTATION.

  METHOD setTotalValue.

    "Read Line Item detail
    READ ENTITIES OF zr_salesorder_head_m IN LOCAL MODE
    ENTITY Item
    FIELDS ( Salesorder Item Rate )
    WITH CORRESPONDING #( keys )
    RESULT DATA(lt_itemrate) .

    IF lt_itemrate IS NOT INITIAL.

      "Write Sales Order Line item = Quantity * Per Unit Price
      MODIFY ENTITIES OF zr_salesorder_head_m IN LOCAL MODE
      ENTITY Item
      UPDATE FIELDS ( Value )
      WITH VALUE #( FOR ls_rate IN lt_itemrate
                  ( %tky = ls_rate-%tky
                    Value = COND #( WHEN ls_rate-Quantity NE 0 AND ls_rate-Rate NE 0
                                    THEN ls_rate-Quantity * ls_rate-Rate
                                    ELSE 0 ) ) ).


    ENDIF.

  ENDMETHOD.

  METHOD setTotalAmount.

    "Read Associated Sales Order Line item Detail
    READ ENTITIES OF zr_salesorder_head_m IN LOCAL MODE
    ENTITY Header
    FIELDS ( SalesOrder )
    WITH CORRESPONDING #( keys )"
    RESULT DATA(lt_head).

    IF lt_head[] IS NOT INITIAL.

      " Trigger Re-Calculation on Sales Order Header Root Node
      MODIFY ENTITIES OF zr_salesorder_head_m IN LOCAL MODE
      ENTITY Header
      EXECUTE reCalculateTotalAmt
      FROM CORRESPONDING #( lt_head ).

    ENDIF.

  ENDMETHOD.

ENDCLASS.


